trans-unit.source: A replacement for dict using hopscotch hashing
trans-unit.target: ホップスコッチハッシュを用いた dict の置換

trans-unit.source: Hopscotch hashing provides a number of benefits over the methods used in the standard dict implementation, most notably that insertions, deletions and lookups have an expected O(1) runtime.
trans-unit.target: Hopscotch hashing provides a number of benefits over the methods used in the standard dict implementation, most notably that insertions, deletions and lookups have an expected O(1) runtime.
ハップスコッチディクショナリ

trans-unit.source: py-hopscotch-dict has not been tested in a concurrent environment and thusly cannot be guaranteed to function correctly in conjunction with multi-threading, across multiple processes or in an asynchronous environment
trans-unit.target: py-hopscotch-dictは並列環境ではテストされていないため、マルチスレッド、複数プロセス、非同期環境での動作を保証するものではありません。

trans-unit.source: py-hopscotch-dict is a package that contains a replacement for the standard Python dict which implements the concepts of hopscotch hashing, as explained in the foundational paper.
trans-unit.target: py-hopscotch-dict is a package that contains a replacement for the standard Python dict which implements the concepts of hopscotch hashing, as explained in the foundational paper.

trans-unit.source: py-hopscotch-dict is implemented to replicate a Python 3.6-style dict, and as such brings additional effects to Python 2.7 beyond those of hopscotch hashing.
trans-unit.target: py-hopscotch-dict is implemented to replicate a Python 3.6-style dict , and as such brings additional effects to Python 2.7 beyond those of hopscotch hashing.
